snippet.title: Sneaky Seekers - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Gold and treasure are waiting for you, will you answer the call?

Here is the first gameplay trailer of Sneaky Seekers, our upcoming chaotic 2D party game for up to 4 players. 
Today, we present you our 3 first mini-games : 
Gold n' Mole, Temple Plunderers, and Treasure Hunt !

Wishlist the game on Steam :
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2459850/Sneaky_Seekers/

Follow us on twitter for more news & content :
https://twitter.com/LavascriptStud
